<h1>Cheap Labor Came at a High Price in 2014</h1>

<p><b>Hong Kong, January 14, 2015</b> – AsiaInspection (AI), a leading global quality control and compliance service provider that partners with brands, retailers and importers around the world to secure, manage and optimize their supply chain, today announces its 2015 Q1 Barometer, a quarterly synopsis on outsourced manufacturing and the quality control services industry.</p>

